creator: Casino Modeling
descriptionHtml:
Do not record the number on the paper anymore!
You can record all numbers of Sicbo forever in any game anywhere.

You can see the recorded numbers in graph form or data in various formats.

Define your own betting pattern, and then when the pattern would be shown, you can see the pattern.
1. Go to the casino setting page.
2. You can define you own betting pattern.
3. There are Big Eye pattern, Big Road pattern, Small Road pattern and Cockroach Pig pattern.
4. When the defined pattern would be shown while you input the value, you can see the Next value of the pattern.


You can see the statistical data following betting rules through analysis on the "menu -> Analysis".

There are betting rules as like Martin Gale rule and Fibonacci rule

Even though you would not bet your money, you can simulate your money to real SicBo game so you can prove your betting style and play practical rehearsal game before playing real game.

Enjoy your game and WIN the game!!!

---------- Disclaimer ---------
This software developed is a recording aid for gamers and does not serve as a guide to a way of winning at the game of Sicbo. The odds at any casino and game is always against the gamer and the developer have no any responsibilities of any losses resulting from the use of the software.

container.value: 3rd floor, AnyMedia bld, 13, Teheran-ro 8-gil, Gangnam-gu, Seoul, Korea

creator: Casino Modeling
descriptionHtml:
Do not record the number on the paper anymore!
You can record all numbers of Sicbo forever in any game anywhere.

You can see the recorded numbers in graph form or data in various formats.

Define your own betting pattern, and then when the pattern would be shown, you can see the pattern.
1. Go to the casino setting page.
2. You can define you own betting pattern.
3. There are Big Eye pattern, Big Road pattern, Small Road pattern and Cockroach Pig pattern.
4. When the defined pattern would be shown while you input the value, you can see the Next value of the pattern.


You can see the statistical data following betting rules through analysis on the "menu -> Analysis".

There are betting rules as like Martin Gale rule and Fibonacci rule

Even though you would not bet your money, you can simulate your money to real SicBo game so you can prove your betting style and play practical rehearsal game before playing real game.

Enjoy your game and WIN the game!!!

---------- Disclaimer ---------
This software developed is a recording aid for gamers and does not serve as a guide to a way of winning at the game of Sicbo. The odds at any casino and game is always against the gamer and the developer have no any responsibilities of any losses resulting from the use of the software.

title: SicBo Analyzer

container.value: 3rd floor, AnyMedia bld, 13, Teheran-ro 8-gil, Gangnam-gu, Seoul, Korea

creator: Casino Modeling
descriptionHtml:
Do not record the number on the paper anymore!
You can record all numbers of Sicbo forever in any game anywhere.

You can see the recorded numbers in graph form or data in various formats.

Define your own betting pattern, and then when the pattern would be shown, you can see the pattern.
1. Go to the casino setting page.
2. You can define you own betting pattern.
3. There are Big Eye pattern, Big Road pattern, Small Road pattern and Cockroach Pig pattern.
4. When the defined pattern would be shown while you input the value, you can see the Next value of the pattern.


You can see the statistical data following betting rules through analysis on the "menu -> Analysis".

There are betting rules as like Martin Gale rule and Fibonacci rule

Enjoy your game and WIN the game!!!

---------- Disclaimer ---------
This software developed is a recording aid for gamers and does not serve as a guide to a way of winning at the game of Sicbo. The odds at any casino and game is always against the gamer and the developer have no any responsibilities of any losses resulting from the use of the software.
-------------------------------------
